lead_paragraph: Defending champion Richard Gasquet of France defeated Marcos Baghdatis of Cyprus 6-4, 6-4 to reach the Open Sud de France semifinals on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Gasquet & German Teen Zverev Reach Open Sud De France Semis
